n december  with the title of commendatore dellordine della stella ditalia personal lifeedit zacconi is married with one son referencesedit  riccardo zacconi king digital entertainment europeanceocom  august    who are the candy crush millionaires guardian   riccardo zacconi king digital entertainment europeanceocom  august    executive profile riccardo zacconi bloomberg   sunday interview kings riccardo zacconi daily telegraph  june    executive profile riccardo zacconi bloomberg   who are the candy crush millionaires guardian   riccardo zacconi king digital entertainment europeanceocom  august    who are the candy crush millionaires guardian   sunday interview kings riccardo zacconi daily telegraph  june    who are the candy crush millionaires guardian   sunday interview kings riccardo zacconi daily telegraph  june    httpwwwamblondraesteriitambasciatalondraenambasciataufficiostampanewsriccardozacconikingentertainmenthtml  sunday interview kings riccardo zacconi daily telegraph  june   retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlericcardozacconioldid categories living peopleitalian businesspeople birthshidden categories articles with hcards navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages add links this page was last edited on  march  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the terms of use and privacy policy wikipedia® is a registered trademark of the wikimedia foundation inc a nonprofit organizatio