lting group between  and  his first career role was as a consultant during a two year long stint at lek consulting between  and  at the start of the dotcom boom in  zacconi joined the swedish online messaging startup spray before it was purchased by lycos europe in  in  he left spray and moved to the uk to become vice president of european sales and marketing at terrence lee zehrers udate he left this company shortly after its merger with matchcom and in march  he cofounded king digital entertainment becoming the ceo he has since grown the company into one of the most successful mobile gaming businesses worldwide media profileedit zacconi is a leading figure in the uk tech industry and is a proponent of the uk governments efforts to establish a tech city in east london according to an interview in the daily telegraph he also has a positive reputation in san francisco as a leading tech figure following a dinner with mark zuckerberg he was reportedly identified as the posterchild for europes mobile gaming sector he was knighted by the italian president in december  with the title of commendatore dellordine della stella ditalia personal lifeedit zacconi is married with one son referencesedit  riccardo zacconi king digital entertainment europeanceocom  august    who are the candy crush millionaires guardian   riccardo zacconi king digital entertainment europeanceocom  august    executive profile riccardo zacconi bloomberg   sunday interview kings riccardo zacconi daily telegraph  june    executive profile riccardo zacconi bloomberg   who are the candy crush millionaires guardian   riccardo zacconi king digital entertainment europeanceocom  august    who are the candy crush millionaires guardian   sunday interview kings riccardo zacconi daily telegraph  june    who are the candy crush millionaires guardian   sunday interview kings riccardo zacconi daily telegraph  june    httpwwwamblondraesteriitambasciatalondraenambasciataufficiostampanewsriccardozacconikingentertainmen