sed to be jungle bubble he’s currently deciding on his new favourite king game  companies in career na related markets  colleagues  related investments alias na industry graphic design services tags entrepreneurship startups new business development venture capital topics of influence na blog careers achievements investments related people edit view all riccardo zacconicareer   king digital entertainment ceo  cofounder aug to mar udate vp europe oct to aug benchmark capital entrepreneur in residence  to  spray network md  to  boston consulting group project manager  to  lek consulting consultant competencies edit view all riccardo zacconieducation luiss university economics edit riccardo zacconiachievements and recognitions add milestone no milestones has been recorded for riccardo zacconi edit view all riccardo zacconilinks  riccardo zacconi  kingcom looking for growth rather than flotation  telegraph source wwwtelegraphcouk wed sep   by spoke mobile research share kingcom ceo riccardo zacconi discusses the future of casual gaming  forbes source wwwforbescom wed sep   by spoke mobile research share view all riccardo zacconiinvestmentsacquisitions  dubsmash since aug series a company status private typeform since sep series a company status private carfoldio since feb series aa company status private riccardo zacconiinvestments representing others no investment reps has been recorded for riccardo zacconi riccardo zacconirelated people colleagues at king digital entertainment lars jörnow vp king labs dec ciara smyth chief people officer oct rob miller chief legal officer and corporate secretary aug alex dale chief marketing officer oct view all peers  bryan mistele founder  ceo of inrix kevin systrom ceo cofounder of instagram cyriac roeding cofounder and ceo of shopkick micah adler ceo and founder of fiksu naveen tewari founder  ceo of inmobi suleman ali angel investor of startups view all riccardo zacconirecommended market profiles  mobile apps  international growt